episodes.title: Justice Department says it needs to go through more Epstein files
episodes.description:
Democrats in Congress say they are planning to take legal action if the Department of Justice does not release the remaining Jeffrey Epstein files. On Wednesday, the DOJ says it uncovered over 1 billion additional documents.

episodes.title: Michigan church  leader charged with criminal sexual conduct
episodes.description: A 29-year-old Washtenaw County church employee was arraigned on several charges, including criminal sexual conduct and charges related to child sexually abusive material.
